 Angulo\n|----- bgcolor=\"#D0E7FF\"\n|'''Conquis XVI'''\n|align=\"center\"|2020\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n== Audience ==\n\n{|class= taulapolita\n|- bgcolor=\"MediumSlateBlue\" style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"\n!Date!!chapter!!Program characteristics!!audience!!Share\n|- \n| 8 January 2007\n| 1. and 2. programs\n| presentation, tema selection,<br /> designation and expulsion\n| 126.000\n| %13,8\n|- bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n| 15 January 2007\n| 3. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 150.000\n| %16,9\n|-\n| 22 January 2007\n| 4. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 148.000\n| %17,5\n|-bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n| 29 January 2007\n| 5. program\n| designation and expulsion \n| 142.000\n| %15,9\n|-\n| 5 February 2007\n| 6. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 152.000\n| %16,7\n|-bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n| 12 February 2007\n| 7. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 152.000\n| %16,4\n|-\n| 19 February 2007\n| 8. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 145.000\n| %16,6\n|-bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n| 26 February 2007\n| 9.program \n| designation and expulsion\n| 142.000\n| %15,7\n|-\n| 5 March 2007\n| 10. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 135.000\n| %16,2\n|-bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n| 12 March 2007\n| 11. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 141.000\n| %16,3\n|-\n| 19 March 2007\n| 12. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 168.000\n| %19,8\n|-bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n| 26 March 2007\n| 13. program\n| designation and expulsion\n| 156.000\n| %18,3\n|-\n| 2 April 2007\n| 14. program\n| designation and expulsion \n| 169.000\n| %18,5\n|-bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n|9 April 2007\n| 15. program\n| designation and expulsion \n| 124.000\n| %16,0\n|-\n| 16 April 2007\n| 16. program \n| designation and expulsion\n| 166.000\n| %17,5\n|-bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n| 23 April 2007\n| 17. program \n| Final\n| 143.000\n| %17,8\n|-\n|}\n\n{|class= taulapolita\n|- bgcolor=\"MediumSlateBlue\" style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"\n!Date!!chapter!!Program characteristics!!audience!!Share\n|- \n| January 12 2009\n| 1. and 2. programs\n| presentation,